      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-athar-husain-rizvi-&-sayed-maqsood-athar": [
          "1. My father (rh) said that 'Abdullah bin Ja'far narrated to me, from Muhammad bin 'Isa, form al-Qasim bin Yahya, from his grandfather al-Hasan bin Rashid, from Abi Basir, form Abu 'Abdillah (a.s.) who said: \"Amir al-Mu'mineen (a.s.) said, “Noorah is an amulet and purity for the body.”\""
        ]
